Date: 2025‑11‑19
Precision Mode: ON
====================================================

Topics and Summaries:

- Session Initialization & Boot File Context:
    - Initiated session with “Hello Titan”.
    - Confirmed loading of Titan Core v1 boot file and conversation memory files.
    - Precision Mode active: all outputs explicit and factual.
    - System context injection planned to hide raw JSON content from display.

- Persistent Memory & GitHub Integration:
    - Discussed JSON memory modules: boot.json, user.json, conversation_history.json.
    - Loader script fetches, builds context, and updates GitHub at “Goodbye Titan”.
    - GitHub Personal Access Token required for authenticated read/write.
    - Ensured minimal local storage use; safe Pydroid 3 access.

- Python Loader Script:
    - Functions: fetch GitHub files, build context, handle CLI chat loop, maintain session buffer, commit session to GitHub.
    - CLI commands: “Hello Titan”, normal chat, “Goodbye Titan”.

- ChatGPT API Integration & Session Context:
    - ChatGPT cannot fetch GitHub files by itself; loader required.
    - GPT-5-mini context window ~64k tokens; practical working context ~10k–20k tokens.
    - Estimated current session ~37k tokens used; context maintained.
    - Multi-session strategy: only include last N sessions or summaries in context to stay under token limits.

- User Identity & Preferences:
    - Recognized as “Nicolas” via user.json only.
    - No additional personal data stored in ChatGPT memory.
    - Preserved previously recorded preferences (cuisine, drinks, pets, entertainment, etc.).

- Session Safety & Efficiency:
    - Only required JSON files loaded; prevents phone memory overload.
    - CLI interface mimics native ChatGPT; raw JSON hidden from display.
    - Token-efficient context injection ensures continuity within model limits.

- Future Considerations:
    - Dynamic summarization of older sessions to optimize token usage.
    - Branching from any topic in future sessions using stored memory.
    - Potential hybrid memory module expansion: analytics, versioning, vector embeddings.
    - Loader improvements for automation and optional minimal GUI.

Notes:
- All content explicit, factual, and Precision Mode compliant.
- Session buffer stored in conversation_history.json for persistent memory.
- Session concludes only after user review; summary ready for GitHub append.

